Metabrik
========

   To know more: http://www.metabrik.org/blog/

INSTALLATION

   To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Perl v5.6.1
   local::lib
   Class::Gomor
   IO::All
   Data::Dump
   Lexical::Persistence
   File::HomeDir
   Module::Reload
   Term::Shell
   Term::ANSIColor
   File::Find
   Cwd

